{
  "stem": "17044.3",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 247.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "They're checking you, also, the documents.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I had to wait the same thing.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Not when then, when a lot of people get together will try to push themselves out.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "A lot of people, in between I sneaked out.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I don't know what chance I took.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And-- so I didn't know where to go, so I figured I'd go back to Vinnitsa to meet this woman.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Maybe she will explain me more this.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So I'm went by railway, went back there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I went back to this town of Vinnitsa.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "All of a sudden I got acquainted with street gangs, street gangs, you know, for stealing, begging, and this.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And they slept in the old broken stores.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And they weren't suspicious.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "There know my name is Andre.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And that's what [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "One guy one day comes in to me and said to me, is you Jewish?",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I said, no.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Why-- why would you make you to think I'm Jewish?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Don't be afraid.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "I'm half Jewish.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "So I was thinking to me, I never heard of such a thing, half Jewish.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Oh, you're Jewish, or you're not Jewish.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "I never heard, from my time, I never heard of thing.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "I didn't tell him this, but I-- I wouldn't admit.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "So you didn't pay attention even-- but his friends, probably they were talking over, one day in the morning to bringing in the police to me, to bring in police to me.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And they tell me, you're Jewish?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "I said no, the policeman.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "They said, say 'kukurydza.' 'Kukurydza' because the Russian Jews, they talk with the throat.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "Oh,",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Not that the tongue.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So I say it correct, 'kukurydza,' [TRILLS AN 'R'] Now, they say, say 'orzel.' 'Kukurydza' means popcorn, and 'orzel' means eagle.",
      "word_count": 21
    }
  ],
